Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隐隐约约察觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我在蔻蔻面前不会笑一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔻蔻则为了掩盖一切而永远把微笑挂在脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约拿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 约拿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太突然了 真的是太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然没电了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是该换电池的时候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不介意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还觉得蛮好玩的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道蔻蔻作为商人手段高超
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她像一个用不平衡的姿势不断全力冲刺的跑者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来有些危险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.63,0:00:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄完了这个也马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约拿小弟飞过来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩丢约拿小弟的游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看谁能丢得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约拿好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔻蔻 还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 人不是用来让你们这么丢着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和武器商人在一起旅行

Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:41.21,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:41.21,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們始终踱步于境界线之上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:43.93,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying the view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:43.93,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆因此境风景独好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:46.55,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eeny,meeny,miny,moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:46.55,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一，二，三，四...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:49.49,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,much the same
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:49.49,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:51.75,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:51.75,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們始终踱步于境界线之上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:55.03,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying the view from here.
