Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:15.53,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pike or shield?  負けたくはない　でも傷つけたくもない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:15.53,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矛 or 盾？ 不想认输 可是又不愿受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.52,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手に取って　確かめてた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.52,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先挑一样在手中仔细掂量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.72,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと戻れないんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.72,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是发现再要反悔为时已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:26.17,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:26.17,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选的是哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.95,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思い出は枷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.95,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思念是枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.47,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  後付けのlove
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.47,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  追悔莫及的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:34.28,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  優しさは仇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:34.28,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  温柔是弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.64,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.64,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们始终踱步于境界线之上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.33,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,広げる両手　keep balance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.33,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张开双臂保持平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:46.56,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,より高く飛べる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:46.56,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着更高的天空振臂而飞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:56.21,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守りたいよ 僕らの翼のないこの背中に背負った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:56.21,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯独想保护的是.. 背负于我们那折翼的背膀之上的
